 the RRAR motif. Therefore, we concluded that the human SARS-CoV-2 virus, which is responsible for the recent outbreak of COVID-19, did not come directly from pangolins.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Li, Xingguang", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Zai, Junjie", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Zhao, Qiang", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Nie, Qing", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Li, Yi", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Foley, Brian T.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chaillon, Antoine", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["COVID-19", "SARS-CoV-2", "TMRCA", "cross-species transmission", "evolutionary rate", "potential intermediate animal host", "Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/06e4e1fddf5c4a7d0c2195102837b8e9", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/797cd581e3d8dc7798fa01f282c1cd04382b0f3cfc716725dea3ddf0d5d3a455", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/8AJYWCLB", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/8AJYWCLB", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/e68d5d5aa0969c149461f822fe5f8d47!/b223749-226379", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"title": "Journal of Medical Virology"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/06e4e1fddf5c4a7d0c2195102837b8e9"}, {"identifier":